snippet.title: DIOR大穎 - LOUISE - (Official MV）
snippet.description:
今天是我們認識的第三個月
I wrote a song for my friend👭



This is a simple story I’d like to share with all of you！

Back in June this year, when I wasn’t in the best place emotionally, I went to London to study. 
That’s where I met a classmate （LOUISE）
who unexpectedly became a very close friend.

We only spent three weeks together,
but it felt like fate — as if she was an angel sent to remind me
that the world is so much bigger, with so many things worth chasing.
So, I wrote this song to remember that time, 
to celebrate the moment I found clarity in myself, 
and to treasure every encounter that leads to the next meeting.

Because our English wasn’t great, that’s why we ended up in the same class in London HAHAHAH
We even promised to go to Australia next year for two more months of English lessons together, to keep growing into better versions of ourselves！

That’s also why this is the very first English song I’ve ever written 
I really using up all the vocabulary I know, haha.

Anyways! Thank you so much for listening to my music and my story.
My name is Dior, and I’m a singer-songwriter from Malaysia,Johor,Batu Pahat,Rengit. 
I’M A KAMPUNG GIRL!

I never imagined myself
stepping into the world of English songs.

But maybe… that’s what life is about.
You’ll never know where the road takes you
unless you keep moving forward.

So, whatever you’re going through,
let the wind carry you onward. ✨




《Louise》
作詞：DIOR大穎
作曲：DIOR大穎
演唱：DIOR大穎、LOUISE

I met an angel
Oh her name is Louise
She’s only just turned eighteen
Oh she’s still chasing her dream

It’s not easy to find a friendship like this
Even though we only had a few weeks
But it still means a lot to me

Ohh girl, you don’t know how much you healed me
You woke a part I couldn’t see
You never know
You never know
You let me be 

We said goodbye till we meet again
And said goodbye but it’s not the end
Said goodbye, remember us this way
Till the end
All the little things with you I won’t forget

Let me tell you a secret
We don’t care what you think
Maybe we got a little crazy
But life is still young
We‘re born to be free

Take it easy
Try to live it wild and free
Sometimes life - a little hazy
So maybe just let it be

Oh girl, you don’t know how much you healed me
You woke a part I couldn’t see
You never know
you never know
你讓我成為自己

We said goodbye till we meet again
And said goodbye but it’s not the end
Said goodbye, remember us this way
Till the end
All the little things with you I won’t forget

Goodbye till we meet again
And said goodbye but it’s not the end
Said goodbye, remember us this way
Till the end
All the little things with you I won’t forget

Let‘s say goodbye till we meet again
And say goodbye but it’s not the end
Say goodbye, remember us this way
Till the end
Day by day we stay the same
See you again
